# Managed files whose conventional or tool-mandated paths are outside .riprap/managed.
# Paths ending in /** authorize every file beneath that directory.
#
# Every file listed here carries the "Riprap-managed" marker among its leading lines, so its
# ownership is visible from the file itself. A path followed by "marker-exempt" is in a format with
# no comment syntax and therefore carries no marker; only comment-less formats may be exempt.
.agents/skills/**
.claude/settings.json	marker-exempt
.claude/skills/**
.codex/hooks.json	marker-exempt
.gitattributes
.gitignore
rr.bat
rr.sh
